channel.title: Need partner [Co-owner]
channel.description:
I am looking for a co owner to my server. It's InsidiaX source. I am not really good at coding, but I know the basics. I got money enough to pay for vps and a domain. I am looking for a partner who got experience with coding and such. My partner doesn't need to help me pay for the server, but some help wouldn't hurt.
It's an economy/pvp based server.
Add me at skype: David.birkelund
